Hello Dearest,

Greetings my dear, i hope this email finds you well.
Let me start by introducing myself to you, I am Mrs. Elizabeth Castro,
manager in auditing department with United Bank for Africa (UBA) Burkina
Faso.
I have a business deal that will be of immense benefit to both of
us if only you will incline to the proposal and keep it confidential,
I discovered a dormant account amounting to USD$11.3million dollar
which belong to a deceased customer of this bank. Late Moises Saba Masri,
a billionaire Business Mogul a Jew from Mexico who was a victim of a
helicopter crash.
See site: ( http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3832556,00.html ).
I cannot do this transaction all alone without employing a foreigner
who will stand as the deceased next of kin, as bank procedure demands.

I shall give you further details about him upon receiving your response.
Please keep this proposal as a top secret and delete if you are not
interested.

Thanks as i await your timely response to my private email address;
( elizabethcastro6453@gmail.com )

My Pleasure
Mrs. Elizabeth Castro.
